OL,3,CMan admits causing death of woman and
OL,4,Cbaby in horror crash
OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to causing
OL,7,Fthe death of a woman and a baby in a
OL,8,Fcrash.
OL,10,FDarryl Anderson, 38, was driving his
OL,11,FAudi Q5 when he crashed into a Peugeot
OL,12,F308, killing eight-month-old Zackary
OL,13,FBlades and 30-year-old Karlene Warner.
OL,15,FThe fatal collision happened on the
OL,16,FA1(M) between Chester-le-Street and
OL,17,FDurham at around 3.15am on Friday May
OL,18,F31.
