OL,6,FZackary's mother Shalorna Warner, who
OL,7,Fwas driving the Peugeot, was also
OL,8,Finjured in the crash.
OL,10,FDarryl Anderson was arrested at the
OL,11,Fscene and appeared at Durham Crown
OL,12,FCourt by video link on Monday 1 July
OL,13,Fcharged with causing death by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving.
OL,16,FHe pleaded guilty to the charges and
OL,17,Fwas remanded in custody until his
OL,18,Fsentencing on Tuesday 9 July.
