OL,6,FAnderson denied unlawfully possessing
OL,7,Fa knife and an axe at the time of the
OL,8,Fcrash and those not guilty pleas were
OL,9,Faccepted by the prosecution.
OL,11,FAbout 30 members of Zackary and
OL,12,FKarlene's family attended the hearing.
OL,14,FJudge Joanne Kidd said the family had
OL,15,Fonly just heard some distressing
OL,16,Fdetails about the crash which they
OL,17,Fwere told after it was known Anderson
OL,18,Fwould plead guilty.
